---
const footerLinks = [
	{ href: '/', label: 'Domov' },
	{ href: '/sluzby', label: 'Služby' },
	{ href: '/kontakt', label: 'Kontakt' },
];

const email = 'kontakt@esticode.sk';
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 dark:border-neutral-800 dark:bg-black">
	<section class="py-16 sm:py-24" aria-labelledby="cta-heading">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2
				id="cta-heading"
				class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl dark:text-white"
			>
				Poďme spolu vytvoriť niečo skvelé.
			</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-lg dark:text-neutral-400">
				Napíšte nám a ozveme sa vám do 24 hodín. Bez zbytočných formulárov — priamo e-mailom.
			</p>
			<a
				href={`mailto:${email}`}
				class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-md focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-blue-600 dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:shadow-none dark:hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:shadow-none dark:focus-visible:outline-white"
			>
				Napíšte nám e-mail
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-neutral-800">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<nav class="flex justify-center py-8 sm:py-10" aria-label="Pätička navigácia">
				<ul class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-8">
						{
							footerLinks.map((link) => (
								<li>
									<a
										href={link.href}
										class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 transition-colors hover:text-slate-900 dark:text-neutral-400 dark:hover:text-white"
									>
										{link.label}
									</a>
								</li>
							))
						}
				</ul>
			</nav>
			<p class="pb-8 text-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-neutral-500 sm:pb-10">
				© 2026 Esticode. Všetky práva vyhradené.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
